# Add a legend/guide box at the bottom of the figure
fig.text(0.02, 0.01, '📖 QUICK GUIDE: Scatter plots show if metrics increase with more connections. ' +
         'Dotted line = trend direction (upward=increases, flat=no change). ' +
         'Correlation strength: 🔥Strong (close relationship), ➡️Moderate (some relationship), 〰️Weak (little relationship). ' +
         'Heatmap colors: 🔵Blue=metrics move together, 🔴Red=metrics move opposite.',
         fontsize=9, ha='left', va='bottom', style='normal', color='#222',
